variable:- its a  name given to a memory location where the value is not fixed, it can change with the course of time 
example: int num,
#syntax:
datatype variable_name:
#assignment:-
variable_name=value
## scope of a variable 
-> scope generally speaks about the visibility of variables 
....local variable
....global variable
###local variable
void main()
{
int rollno=10;
}
###global varaiable
int y=50;
